data.title: Aron J Warner - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Aron J Warner: his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

American film producer and voice actor who has lent his voice to characters in the Shrek film franchise and The Book of Life. He has produced films including the Shrek franchise, Antz, Wish Dragon, and The Book of Life. He has 17 producing credits to his name.

Before Fame

He began his career in 1999 with a voice acting role in the video game M.U.G.E.N.

Trivia

He worked on the visual effects for the 2002 film Minority Report. Throughout his career, he has received over ten credits for his acting roles in different films. As well as acting and producing, he has served as Vice President of Productions at Twentieth Century Fox.

Family Life

He was born and raised in the United States.
